From 6f29afd7097867c4a5326f4c4cdcb22e3b53cd8b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arecsu <alejandro9r@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 28 Mar 2026 03:49:09 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 3/5] opencl: implement cl_khr_d3d10_sharing extension for DXVK
 compatibility

Implement the cl_khr_d3d10_sharing OpenCL extension using standard DXGI
interfaces (IDXGIAdapter via dxgi1_6.h) instead of Wine-internal
IWineDXGIAdapter, enabling compatibility with DXVK's DXGI implementation.

This allows Affinity and other applications to discover OpenCL devices
through D3D10/DXGI adapter matching.

Also implements full DXCore adapter enumeration via DXGI with correct
PCI ID reporting.

Based on ElementalWarrior/__avg__ OpenCL patches.

Co-authored-by: James McDonnell <topgamer7@gmail.com>
